//www.findagrave.com/cemetery/2295790/hindes-cemetery","hooker_connections":["H01050","X02572"],"notes":"Hindes Cemetery, Addison, Addison County VT. Burial place of Bela Norton (H01050) and his first wife Lydia Bushnell Norton (X02572). The couple migrated from Connecticut to Cheshire MA (1794) to Addison VT (where Lydia died 1813); Bela later moved on to Mexico NY where he died 1845, but his remains appear to have been returned to Addison."},"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}